ChangeLog

This ChangeLog only lists change after the last release of PHP-UTF8 at 2007-08-12 03:20.

* Version 0.5.1 - Someday XXth, 2010.

  - Cleaned up and reformatted all the functions and tests.
  - Fixed all deprecation errors.
  - Renamed LICENCE to COPYING.
  - Added VERSION for easy version checking.
  - utf8_strpos() and utf8_strrpos() from Mbstring now strip invalid character out of the given string.

  - Added utf8_sprintf/utf8_vprintf to UTF-8 library:
    http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=detail&aid=1804663&group_id=142846&atid=753845
  - Added utf8_wordwrap to UTF-8 library:
    http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=detail&aid=1804661&group_id=142846&atid=753845
  - Added utf8_html_entity_decode to the UTF-8 library:
    http://sourceforge.net/tracker/?func=detail&aid=1783133&group_id=142846&atid=753845
